---
title: Portuguese-Style Chicken Strips & Herbed Brown Rice with Roasted Veggies
description: Take your tastebuds on a trip to Portugal with this colourful feast. An easy marinade on the chicken, veggies
roasted to sweet perfection and smokey aioli is what it's all about.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/portuguese-style-chicken-strips-ad18ad56.jpg
